<h2 class="bold font-l">Asajj Ventress Escapes</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
When preparing to escape the Tranquility, Ventress uses an explosion to propel her down an air vent. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alt-titles section section-fact">
<h3>
<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
<span>Explosive Propulsion</span> </h3>
</div>
